{"tid":1503071,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"發送匣有紅點其實代表乜","createTime":"2019-08-24T20:58:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T21:04:55.000Z","uid":301648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5b63a557ce822ace37a936fa40836ca1ce354ece","tid":1503071,"uid":301648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T20:58:05.000Z","msg":"如題。發送匣有紅點其實係代表乜嘢？<br />\n<br />\n事緣係我有好幾次見到發送匣見到有紅點，恁住有新回覆，點知click咗入去見原來冇新回覆，覺得好奇怪，有咩情況會咁？<br />\n<br />\n係唔係有正負評都會有紅點？定係有block咗嘅人留言？定係其他原因？定係我理解錯咗紅點嘅意思？"},{"pid":"42a79fcf7da020b16a48227c049745023e6f8e4d","tid":1503071,"uid":152222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T21:04:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}